snippet.title: Tanks of Freedom Gameplay
snippet.description:
Tanks of Freedom Gameplay
Well this is an interesting open-source project, this game is an Turn-based strategy game but to be honest I don't see this game growing and becoming better, I just don't see is. well maybe the developers know a way to make it a bigger and better game but for now it is now the best game, however it has a small thrill when you play this game.

You van download this game from official website
http://w84death.itch.io/tanks-of-freedom

Catch up with me on Twitter

https://twitter.com/#!/Studio76HD
Take a look at this page

http://digitalstudio7.blogspot.com/
